<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>About Us - Our Restaurant</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 10px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
}

nav ul li {
    margin: 0 20px;
}

nav ul li a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
}

nav ul li a:hover {
    color: #e67e22;
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
    background-image: url('hero-background.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

.hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3.5em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
}

/* About Section */
.about-section {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
}

.about-container {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    align-items: center;
}

.about-text {
    flex: 1;
}

.about-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about-text p {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    max-width: 400px;
}

/* Mission Section */
.mission {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background-color: #e67e22;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}

.mission-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.mission h2 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.mission p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
}

/* Values Section */
.values {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    text-align: center;
}

.values h2 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.values-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 30px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.value {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    width: 280px;
    text-align: center;
}

.value h3 {
    font-size: 1.8em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.value p {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    color: #555;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
}

footer p {
    font-size: 1em;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./common/header1.ejs') %>

    <section class="hero bg-dark">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Restaurant</h1>
            <p>Your destination for authentic flavors and exceptional service</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Founded in 2015, Our Restaurant is dedicated to bringing the freshest, most flavorful dishes to your table. Our journey began with a passion for high-quality, locally sourced ingredients and a love for crafting unique dining experiences.</p>
                <p>From our humble beginnings, we've grown to become a beloved community staple, known for our friendly atmosphere and diverse menu. Every dish we create tells a story, combining time-honored recipes with modern culinary techniques.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="./images/logo.jpg" alt="Restaurant interior">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
        <div class="mission-container">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Our Restaurant, our mission is to provide every guest with a memorable experience through exceptional food, impeccable service, and a welcoming atmosphere. We aim to foster a sense of community and create lasting connections with each meal.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values">
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <div class="values-container">
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Quality</h3>
                <p>We use only the freshest ingredients, sourced locally whenever possible, to ensure every dish is of the highest quality.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Innovation</h3>
                <p>We are constantly exploring new flavors and techniques, ensuring that every meal is both exciting and delicious.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value">
                <h3>Community</h3>
                <p>We believe in creating an inclusive environment where our guests feel like part of our family, whether they're here for a casual meal or a special celebration.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('./common/fotter.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
